{"tid":984622,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"非洲豬瘟肆虐　長洲東灣泳灘驚現豬屍　","createTime":"2019-01-17T03:05:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-17T04:05:03.000Z","uid":39464,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"abc04bc68a05bb095527d025cc418806688ca398","tid":984622,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T03:05:55.000Z","msg":"長洲東灣泳灘發現豬屍，今早(17日)10時27分，有市民在泳灘上發現一頭約3呎長的死豬屍體，由於擔心是大陸病死豬隻漂洋過海「登陸」，於是報警，警方正封鎖現場調查。 <br />\n<br />\n內地非洲豬瘟爆發情況嚴重，內地曾有24個省份發生過家豬和野豬疫情，累計撲殺生豬91.6萬頭；上月19日，台灣宜蘭縣利澤沙灘亦發現一頭死豬屍體，隨即引起台灣網民恐慌。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190117/bkn-20190117104900135-0117_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190117%2Fbkn-20190117104900135-0117_00822_001.html&d=wupA0mMK9VTR1jnO51Ll3ozZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=4e55f18b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190117/bkn-20190117104900135-0117_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"44e0f4e8f68ff1e23b44b49375e3027d2876b2f6","tid":984622,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T03:07:01.000Z","msg":"2047"},{"pid":"b1105feb424f1dc20a4f741b97b9beb0d1e22f16","tid":984622,"uid":12404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T03:07:31.000Z","msg":"支那送大禮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8003d266892dbdd7c05f7c870bd471bf4c417343","tid":984622,"uid":198583,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T03:07:46.000Z","msg":"希望可以變種到傳染畀人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f4e214108f80e334a99786fb769c55d647e6290","tid":984622,"uid":38757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T03:09:04.000Z","msg":"應該唔會公報出黎,條豬屍有無豬瘟"},{"pid":"c65c29e698b0c41fe06da6f974c7f6eb2044c485","tid":984622,"uid":61511,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"3f4e214108f80e334a99786fb769c55d647e6290","tid":98462